OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA grey start this morning,
OL,6,Fhowever the cloud will gradually lift
OL,7,Fand burn away to leave another sunny
OL,8,Fday.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FRemaining dry and warm
OL,11,Fovernight with plenty of clear skies.
OL,12,FSome patchy cloud however may reform
OL,13,Flater in the night across the east.
OL,14,
OL,15,CMonday:FAny overnight cloud quickly
OL,16,Fclearing to leave a dry and sunny day
OL,17,Facross the region. Feeling very warm
OL,18,Fonce again.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
